Recipe 4: Single-select pills as tab bar with content panels

Use single-select pills as horizontal tabs:

```
<$transclude $tiddler="$:/plugins/rimir/components/pills"
  elements="overview settings logs"
  selection="single"
  sync-tiddler="$:/state/my/tabs"
  sync-field="text"/>

<$reveal type="match" state="$:/state/my/tabs" text="overview">
  Overview content...
</$reveal>
<$reveal type="match" state="$:/state/my/tabs" text="settings">
  Settings content...
</$reveal>
<$reveal type="match" state="$:/state/my/tabs" text="logs">
  Logs content...
</$reveal>
```

---

Recipe 5: Vtabs as navigation with tiddler links

Use `lnk` type to build a navigation sidebar:

```
<$transclude $tiddler="$:/plugins/rimir/components/vtabs"
  elements="Pages $:/myapp/home $:/myapp/settings $:/myapp/about"
  type-fn="[<element>match[Pages]then[sec]]~[[lnk]]"
  state="$:/state/my/nav"
  default-collapsed="no">

  <$fill $name="view-sec">
    <strong><<element>></strong>
  </$fill>

  <$fill $name="view-lnk">
    <$text text={{{[<element>split[/]last[]]}}}/>
  </$fill>
</$transclude>
```

---

Recipe 6: Multi-select pills with action callback

Trigger a side-effect each time a pill is toggled:

```
<$transclude $tiddler="$:/plugins/rimir/components/pills"
  elements="feat-1 feat-2 feat-3"
  selection="multi"
  sync-tiddler="$:/config/features"
  sync-field="enabled">
  <$fill $name="on-select">
    <$action-log message=`Feature $(element)$ toggled`/>
    <!-- Could also call set_field on another tiddler, send a message, etc. -->
  </$fill>
</$transclude>
```

---

Recipe 7: Dynamic elements from wiki data

Elements can come from any source — pre-compute them with `$let`:

```
<!-- Pills from all tiddlers tagged "Project" -->
<$let project-list={{{[tag[Project]sort[title]join[ ]]}}}>
<$transclude $tiddler="$:/plugins/rimir/components/pills"
  elements=<<project-list>>
  selection="single"
  sync-tiddler="$:/state/active-project">
  <$fill $name="view">
    <$text text={{{[<element>get[caption]else<element>]}}}/>
  </$fill>
</$transclude>
</$let>
```

---

Recipe 8: Combining pills and vtabs for master-detail

Horizontal pill tabs select a category, vtabs shows items in that category:

```
<$transclude $tiddler="$:/plugins/rimir/components/pills"
  elements="tools settings info"
  selection="single"
  sync-tiddler="$:/state/category"
  sync-field="text"/>

<$reveal type="match" state="$:/state/category" text="tools">
<$transclude $tiddler="$:/plugins/rimir/components/vtabs"
  elements="section tool-a tool-b tool-c"
  type-fn="[<element>match[section]then[sec]]~[[act]]"
  state="$:/state/tools-vtabs"
  default-collapsed="no">
  <$fill $name="view-sec"><strong>Tools</strong></$fill>
  <$fill $name="view-act">&#9654; <<element>></$fill>
</$transclude>
</$reveal>
```

